            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            初教6与陆基模拟着舰          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                                                                    <span role="link" tabindex="0" id="js_author_name" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta_link weui-wa-hotarea" datarewardsn="" datatimestamp="" datacanreward="0">航空小筑的方方</span>                                                                            </span>                                                                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                方方的航空小筑              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">方方的航空小筑</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">ffaerofield</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">航迷自留地。非官宣消息都不知道。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100014308" data-ratio="0.5623188405797102" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/BkRwYcxqDH7sCt8dO4jH8EDDClssaj0eHGyvu5ibILg0Voad1d5FDiaibpUblSZHwUo7vbFfGqZq8ELnoJTzgIfcQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="690" style=""></p><p>        前几天央视报道：<span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>海军航空大学某团紧贴实战，聚焦舰载，创新开展了舰载化培养模式，力争最大化还原舰机训练流程。在报道视频中，菲涅尔透镜旁边，出现了初教-6的身影。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-size: 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;'>        </span><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>对于着舰训练前移到初教6阶段，说点个人看法。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>        首先，初教6自身的特点。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>        初教6是活塞动力螺旋桨飞机，这个特点使得它在操纵上面和学员未来要飞的典型喷气式飞机有较大差异。当年教8论证的时候就提过这一条，避免学员在初教6上养成痼癖动作。后来在是否引进PC-7/9作为中教的讨论中也有这一条。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>        所以对于喷气机学员来说，初教6都不是真正的“教练机”，它不是用来对飞行操纵技能养成和提高的。不管初教6飞什么科目，都不会是长期训练。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>        第二，“筛选教练机”<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>        <span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>“筛选教练机”并不是一个专用名词，但用在初教6身上很合适。初教6的设计很不错，操纵性、安全性都很好，属于那种上天后只要你不作死就不会死的飞机。对于新手上路的学员来说，确实相当友好。所以在以前，无论空军还是海军，都是用来筛选具备较好飞行潜质的飞行学员的。<br></span></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>        第三，时不我待<br></span></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>        去年央视采访一位飞行教员，这位教员提到，以前我们是培养有潜质的飞行员，现在我们是挑选本身已经具备优秀特质的学员来培养。这两者的关键差别就是成长时间。<br></span></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>        第四，层层递进<br></span></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>        在官方的媒体报道中，海军航空大学进行陆基模拟着舰训练，最早的机型是歼15，然后是海山鹰/海山鹰改，再然后就是教8。<br></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100014309" data-ratio="0.5861148197596796" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/BkRwYcxqDH7sCt8dO4jH8EDDClssaj0eZSad0ujeIZCEYTHiaLicDpoXibvva4ypLgx0skWNcay6xPWx8mhJZJa7g/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="1498" style=""></p><p>        这是2019年中国军网的报道。报道最后提及，<span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'>模拟陆基起降训练已经写入该型高教机训练大纲。<br></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100014310" data-ratio="0.7866756393001346" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/BkRwYcxqDH7sCt8dO4jH8EDDClssaj0e4IGIFJLGyXCcIXnjRqTjiaVamjfmPVFCRjLiasiaGA3wLOod4TQzm2rnA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="1486" style=""></p><p>        结合上面教员的这番话，我们大致可以知道初教6在舰载机飞行员培养体系中的角色了：</p><p>        目前整个培养体系已经基本成型，无论是舰载机部队扩编还是其它方面的需求，我们都需要大量优秀飞行员的补充。传统的潜质培养方式已经不能满足我们对于时间的迫切要求，所以需要利用初教6提前筛选具备舰载机飞行员特质的学员——至于什么样的特质，其实上面的采访已经说到了。</p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;font-size: 17px;'><br></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Noto Sans", sans-serif;font-size: 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: pre-wrap;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;display: inline !important;float: none;'>        </span><br></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="424026001" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
